&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;http://softwareengineering.stackexchange.com/q/340638/116650&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;http://softwareengineering.stackexchange.com/q/340638/116650&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;http://stackoverflow.com/q/11146825/1108891&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

