</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Oct 2016 19:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.muddlingthru.ca:80/to-the-edge-or-how-i-spent-my-summer-vacation-2005</guid></item><item><title>Azure Web App Service and Portal downtime analysis 06 October 2017</title><link>http://www.muddlingthru.ca:80/azure-web-app-service-and-portal-downtime-analysis-06-october-2017</link><description>&lt;h1&gt;TLDR;&lt;/h1&gt;

