&lt;h1&gt;8:30 am PST - 07 Oct 2016&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I open support ticket &lt;code&gt;116100714772026&lt;/code&gt; from the Azure Portal. The ticket asks about two problems: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Deployment options button is broken. &lt;/li&gt;
